cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.DC, cs.SI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with routing algorithms in ad hoc networks. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper proposes a new algorithm for routing. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper may involve information theory concepts in designing the routing algorithm. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is relevant as ad hoc networks are distributed systems. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) may also be relevant as the paper deals with communication in networks.
